          <div class="flex items-center mb-6">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-red-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
              <Target className="w-6 h-6 text-red-600" />
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-red-900">The Problem Most Construction Businesses Face:</h3>
          </div>
          <ul class="space-y-4 text-red-900">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-red-700 mr-3 mt-1 font-bold">•</span>
              <span class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900">No online visibility → missing potential clients</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-red-700 mr-3 mt-1 font-bold">•</span>
              <span class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900">Competitors ranking higher on Google</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-red-700 mr-3 mt-1 font-bold">•</span>
